{"tid":648262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯：同性戀平權教育 毒害下一代","createTime":"2018-04-30T13:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T01:48:53.000Z","uid":134071,"like":12,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8378c4fcf5e8d3edfd07fc5c2dd0b4762e4652e6","tid":648262,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:54:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180430/s00001/1525077360117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180430%2Fs00001%2F1525077360117&d=sa8YgtJdsX6r1gXYSKZ%2FfTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f8a66e9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180430%2Fs00001%2F1525077360117&h=deee4c36\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180430/s00001/1525077360117</a><br />\n<br />\n反對委任兩名外籍女法官　何君堯：兩人撐平權　市民憂損華人文化 (16:47)<br />\n2018/4/30<br />\n<br />\n<strong>政府任命英國最高法院院長何熙怡女男爵（Brenda Hale），及加拿大最高法院前首席法官麥嘉琳（Beverley McLachlin），為終審法院非常任法官。有建制派議員指，兩人均支持同志平權，擔心她們將來審理同性婚姻案件時有偏頗。本身是律師的何君堯，更明言反對兩人任命，稱平權教育毒害下一代，「人類滅亡敲起喪鐘先兆」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n何君堯在facebook直播中指出，傳統家庭是「一男一女一夫一妻」，若容許同性婚姻合法化，「必定會搞到亂七八糟」。而上述兩位法官在平權、同性戀議題方面「好開明」，處理相關案件時必然有很大影響。<br />\n<br />\n他稱聲收到20多位市民來信，表達對任命兩人的擔憂，如影響華人文化、傳統家庭觀及價值觀等，故他要求召開公聽會。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯強調不是干擾司法獨立。至於有人認為委任法官不應政治化，他反駁：「對唔住，委任法官確確實實，本身亦係政治，亦都係行政，我哋檢定同批核，正正係政治化嘅事。」他又說不委任這兩人，不會影響香港處理案件效能及運作，亦不會窒礙香港法律發展。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯續說，平權教育或會「毒害了下一代」，是「人類滅亡敲起喪鐘先兆」。"},{"pid":"ad9ad923a6990a492384f2afd3de7cd57a755ffd","tid":648262,"uid":37869,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"支持恢復傳統文化 一夫多妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb09678ba884702c48953f225594f6f85428972","tid":648262,"uid":24139,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:01:30.000Z","msg":"何妖又亂講野！明明傳統家庭價值係一夫多妻，唔係西洋低等民族侵華，中國仍可保留此優良傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d57451c0ea393b4a8f9b3f0eaa67300cd67a5d6","tid":648262,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"反平權反同性戀<br />\n但又係何妖<br />\n連登仔幫邊邊好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c48b7972cb33f8be98e6f7a1acdd4843f74c400","tid":648262,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d57451c0ea393b4a8f9b3f0eaa67300cd67a5d6","tid":648262,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"反平權反同性戀<br />\n但又係何妖<br />\n連登仔幫邊邊好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"搞掂隻死共狗先，去平機會投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d39d895f898cad022b3922854cd35ecf1cf80c5","tid":648262,"uid":132859,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"平權冇所謂<br />\n唔撚俾佢哋結婚咪得"},{"pid":"b10b28905bea6979bb6b681642bb7c81c09eea85","tid":648262,"uid":88123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:06:23.000Z","msg":"留名睇連登仔內心交戰"},{"pid":"d14b530f1e7a18ee60f662f8ceefe380fcba171e","tid":648262,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"20多位市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cefdeeae44e7fb8c4f7fba61bb9e3e5fa5ad49e","tid":648262,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:08:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb44dd157bd2011314ded1116661c09a0c6560a6","tid":648262,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:09:38.000Z","msg":"熱烈歡迎呢兩位法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab545f38b6d5c8f3fe3e1afce0f67d22e8ae67b5","tid":648262,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:11:39.000Z","msg":"佢係律師咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d44149e1d82f95736588a338f795e7ea475c49","tid":648262,"uid":60366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:12:11.000Z","msg":"中華民族傳統婚姻文化<br />\n一夫多妻，男權主義，扎腳，浸豬籠"},{"pid":"51ea9e77529e0d60901abe8ede6869728d8e7508","tid":648262,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4cefdeeae44e7fb8c4f7fba61bb9e3e5fa5ad49e","tid":648262,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:08:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:19:57.000Z","msg":"話晒都係出名嘅明光社後花園，連登仔點會咁易跪低，幫住何妖先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac716c1de7c216752158e152e75deeb7609a6240","tid":648262,"uid":22609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"何君堯黨中央對着幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【《人民日報》發文稱同性戀屬正常】<br />\n【新浪微博停止清理同性戀內容】<br />\n2018年4月18日<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博上周起，展開為期三個月的清理行動，題材包括涉及色情、血腥暴力和同性戀的漫畫及短片內容。<br />\n<br />\n兩日之後，《人民日報》的微博發表標題為《不一樣的煙火一樣可以綻放》的文章。當中引述一本小學教科書的內容，指同性戀是正常，絕對不是疾病，又指處理網絡內容不可以因急生錯，「眉毛鬍子一把抓」，把同性戀與色情暴力相提並論，難免引來輿論焦慮，似乎是批評新浪微博的清理行動。<br />\n<br />\n文章發表一日後，新浪微博周一宣布清理行動不再針對同性戀內容。有關注同性戀權益的媒體認為，官方報紙第一次為同志發聲是很好的事情，是大眾爭取的成果，接下來希望微博亦會向同志群體做更進一步的說明和道歉。亦有同性戀組織成員認為，事件反映新浪微博過分演繹了《網絡安全法》的準則。<br />\n<br />\n#同性戀<br />\n#人民日報<br />\n#網絡安全法<br />\n#不一樣的煙火<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"19a2b6ea6287ea3dc6a8c68c4748e47c9dc8876b","tid":648262,"uid":99205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/222050_406d25eb7555b8540dae7a686588ba21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F222050_406d25eb7555b8540dae7a686588ba21.jpg&h=33fa471f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五毛分化對象<br />\n<br />\n不同年紀人士, 乜柒X0,Y0後<br />\n不同性別相處問題,包括男女,同性戀<br />\n不同宗教信仰人士<br />\n不同教育人士<br />\n不同階級，職業人士<br />\n不同運動，球隊之fans<br />\n不同言語人士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支那最喜歡內鬥，厚黑</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a6f225c899196f25eb31341308b312fbd23eba73","tid":648262,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"0d39d895f898cad022b3922854cd35ecf1cf80c5","tid":648262,"uid":132859,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"平權冇所謂<br />\n唔撚俾佢哋結婚咪得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:28:45.000Z","msg":"結婚同領養都一定唔得<br />\n破壞香港道德倫理"},{"pid":"9bcad9bdecf2b43295341183fa961b8ab14f3dca","tid":648262,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:30:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e82995cc1a4ca1ad5babdafc7b7a07c698d4818c","tid":648262,"uid":12782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6f225c899196f25eb31341308b312fbd23eba73","tid":648262,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"0d39d895f898cad022b3922854cd35ecf1cf80c5","tid":648262,"uid":132859,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"平權冇所謂<br />\n唔撚俾佢哋結婚咪得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:28:45.000Z","msg":"結婚同領養都一定唔得<br />\n破壞香港道德倫理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:34:13.000Z","msg":"道德倫理邊個規定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef806dbddcda93b699de05db26af7334d7635616","tid":648262,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:35:29.000Z","msg":"係美國審查d大法官既政見正常到仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 侵侵委任個保守法官對家咪有係玩鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n司法係兵家必爭之地，普通刑事案可以好依條文，但上到司法覆核果d野根本政見行先，果d xyz權可以無限延伸。你睇下孔允明案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e01c7b995bd30c884415e0606e0ae628a18d65","tid":648262,"uid":83097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:48:35.000Z","msg":"遲早會殺左何君堯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc376c2e114abd36377d0a3ecd2d84cdc73111a","tid":648262,"uid":139100,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八<br />\n你係基就基 係直就直<br />\n關平唔平權乜嘢事?<br />\n同性婚姻合法 就會直都走去搞基呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反你係基嘅 冇同性婚姻合法 <br />\n你又走去結婚生仔呀?<br />\n搵啲九唔搭八嘅理由反對鬼佬法官<br />\n都係做戲啫"},{"pid":"f656924816f2e9b7f3a032af8a51f28c45c88a5a","tid":648262,"uid":131691,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9dc376c2e114abd36377d0a3ecd2d84cdc73111a","tid":648262,"uid":139100,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八<br />\n你係基就基 係直就直<br />\n關平唔平權乜嘢事?<br />\n同性婚姻合法 就會直都走去搞基呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反你係基嘅 冇同性婚姻合法 <br />\n你又走去結婚生仔呀?<br />\n搵啲九唔搭八嘅理由反對鬼佬法官<br />\n都係做戲啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:32:22.000Z","msg":"可能何君堯真係好想同男人結婚，所以反對。"},{"pid":"417b6e7e1e168bdbf3ede520871024cebaf30166","tid":648262,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T17:53:17.000Z","msg":"高球場隔離啲地申報左未"},{"pid":"b3589999948c544a3816edec81a2f1ff20110a43","tid":648262,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b60173c9431b3286aed9f254fa9ebc1d4c26fb","tid":648262,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:48:53.000Z","msg":"我贊成同性戀 我地呢d毒撚會少d競爭對手